Who We Are


Seva specializes in procurement services for the hospitality industry, with a focus on independent, boutique, luxury and resort properties. As a Seva Procurement member you will not only benefit from highly leveraged pricing on industry leading goods and services, but from our strategic expertise and experience, as well.  Learn More

 



	 







What We Do






 Proprietary e-Procurement Technology SevaNet enables operators to gain control over a fragmented purchasing process and communicate efficiently with suppliers. 




 Procurement & Operational Expertise Seva is not a "book of deals."  With Seva, members gain not only highly leveraged programs, but industry-leading expertise, as well.




Contracted Supplier ProgramsThe heart of the Seva Procurement solution is the portfolio of supplier programs that lower the total cost of goods and services by as much as 20%. 











Supplier Programs





 
Agronomy ProgramWith Seva’s Agronomy Program, gain access to highly leveraged programs on all of your agronomy and grounds maintenance needs.

 

 
Food  Beverage ProgramSeva has highly specialized programs that meet the standards of the most demanding chefs.

 

 
Room Operations ProgramThe Rooms Program is designed to exceed the expectations of even the most discriminating world traveler.

 

 
Administrative ProgramSeva’s Administrative Program provides access to everything they need to keep their businesses running smoothly and efficiently.

 

 
Engineering ProgramThe Seva Engineering Program provides access to all of the maintenance, repair and operational supplies to maintain your properties.

 

 
Spa ProgramYou can relax with Seva’s Spa Program, knowing your property will gain access to the most innovative solutions.

 

 
Financial ServicesThe Seva Financial Services Program provides innovative and cost-cutting solutions to manage many of your financial services needs.

 

 
CapEx ProgramSeva has developed a unique CapEx Program designed to provide valuable expertise and assistance.

 

 
FF&E SolutionsSeva’s FF&E program provides access to comprehensive solutions for all your renovations, remodels and construction projects.

 


 








