SEVA Technology Solutions, Inc $75,000 Financing
SEVA Technology Solutions, Inc just submitted form D announcing $75,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. SEVA Technology Solutions, Inc was able to sell $75,000. That is 100% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $75,000. The financing was made by 1 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-10-04. SEVA Technology Solutions, Inc is based in  1057 E. IMPERIAL HWY. SUITE 195 PLACENTIA 92870. The firm's business is Other Technology. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  Samit Desai.





